  Locus:
    Page: 134
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Evil
---
Nothing which is naturally inevitable can possibly be evil. Winter, night,
death are not evils. They are the natural transitions from one day to
another day, from autumn to spring, from one life to another life.
